- **what we will do**
	- we will start with this [bookstore site](https://et872-bookstore-with-context.vercel.app) build with useContext and useState
	- we will create a page called **Demo** which will be a disconnected demo of useReducer, in order to learn the basics
	- then we will piece-by-piece refactor the appContext **swapping out useState and replacing it with useReducer**
