	- our first middleware in this howto will be a
		- custom middleware, i.e. that we program ourselves
		- application-level, i.e. it is run before every route
		- the purpose of this middleware is to be able to 
			- change a config variable **apiStatus** from **live** to **maintenanceMode** 
			- provide a date time when the site will be up again
			- which will cause all routes to return a message that the site is down and when it will be up
	- create the config file first
