- **>>> 5. Define TypeScript types from Zod schemas**
	- Zod works very well with TypeScript in that you can infer TypeScript types from Zod schemas
		- this enables you to define your typing information in one place
		- Zod only allows us to infer TypeScript types but not interfaces, so let's use types
